Summary:    OSM Scout Server
Version:    1.17.0
Release:    1
Group:      Qt/Qt
License:    GPLv3
URL:        https://github.com/rinigus/osmscout-server
Source0:    %{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
%if 0%{?sailfishos}
